OL,3,CHungry burglar caught eating sandwich
OL,4,Cinside flat he had broken into
OL,6,FThis is the moment a hungry burglar
OL,7,Fwas captured by police after he was
OL,8,Ffound munching down on a sandwich in a
OL,9,FNottingham flat he had broken into.
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Police found 33-year-
OL,12,Fold Costin Stan with stolen jewellery
OL,13,Fin his pockets after residents at the
OL,14,Fflat in Gregory Boulevard reported
OL,15,Fsomeone trespassing in their home on
OL,16,F23 November.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
