CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772549420
OL,3,CHungry burglar caught eating sandwich
OL,4,Cinside flat he had broken into
OL,6,FThe couple told officers they had come
OL,7,Fface-to-face with Stan on their
OL,8,Fupstairs landing, when he asked for
OL,9,Ffood. He denied that he had broken
OL,10,Finto the flat in order to steal.
OL,12,FStan was given a sandwich, but the
OL,13,Fcouple, who were at home with their
OL,14,Fchildren, then noticed jewellery had
OL,15,Fbeen taken from a bedroom drawer.
OL,17,FOfficers arrived and found Stan sat in
OL,18,Fthe kitchen eating a sandwich. They
OL,19,Fthen discovered the missing jewellery
OL,20,Fin his pockets during searches and
OL,21,FStan was arrested for burglary.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772549420
OL,3,CHungry burglar caught eating sandwich
OL,4,Cinside flat he had broken into
OL,6,FInvestigations revealed he was also
OL,7,Fresponsible for a break-in at another
OL,8,Faddress, in Norton Street, in Radford,
OL,9,Ften days earlier.
OL,11,FThe homeowners had awoken to discover
OL,12,Ftheir flat had been ransacked while
OL,13,Fthey slept.
OL,15,FA host of items, including mobile
OL,16,Fphones, hair straighteners, wallets
OL,17,Fand clothing were missing, and the
OL,18,Fflat had been untidily searched.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772549420
OL,3,CHungry burglar caught eating sandwich
OL,4,Cinside flat he had broken into
OL,6,FStan's fingerprints were found on
OL,7,Fproperty when forensic investigators
OL,8,Fattended the scene.
OL,10,FHe pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,11,Fburglary.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FAt Nottingham Crown Court on Wednesday
OL,19,F(25 February) he was jailed for a
OL,20,Ftotal of two years and eight months.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
