OL,3,CHungry burglar caught eating sandwich
OL,4,Cinside flat he had broken into
OL,6,FInvestigator Bethany Harding, of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "The
OL,8,Fvictims in both these burglaries were
OL,9,Fat home when Stan broke into their
OL,10,Fproperty in order to steal.
OL,12,F"The unusual nature of his arrest
OL,13,Fshould not take away from the
OL,14,Fseriousness of his offending.
OL,16,F"Burglary is an invasive crime which
OL,17,Fcan have a lasting and profound impact
OL,18,Fon any victim.
OL,26,@oD@_OUtD@AOUxD@AOU
