PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772549420
OL,3,CHungry burglar caught eating sandwich
OL,4,Cinside flat he had broken into
OL,6,F"Officers worked hard to ensure he had
OL,7,Fno choice but to admit both these
OL,8,Foffences and I'm pleased he has now
OL,9,Fbeen handed a custodial sentence."
